        <p><strong>19.2</strong> Electronic communications satisfy any legal requirement for communication to be in writing, in accordance with the Electronic Transactions Act 2002.</p>
        <p><strong>19.3</strong> You may opt out of marketing communications at any time. However, you may not opt out of transactional communications required for the servicing of your EPM or those required by law.</p>
        <p><strong>19.4</strong> You are responsible for ensuring your email address and contact details are up to date. We are not liable for any failure of communication due to incorrect contact details.</p>
