        <h2>21. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p><strong>21.1</strong> To the maximum extent permitted by law, FutureProof's aggregate liability to you under or in connection with these Terms, the Platform, or any EPM product is limited to the total fees paid by you to FutureProof in the 12 months preceding the claim.</p>
