        <h2>23. Amendments</h2>
        <p><strong>23.1</strong> We may amend these Terms from time to time. Material amendments will be notified to you at least 30 days in advance via email or Platform notification.</p>
        <p><strong>23.2</strong> If you do not agree with the amended Terms, you may close your account before the amendments take effect. Continued use of the Platform after the effective date of any amendment constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>
